      "value": "<p>Originally created for great vesk commanders during the Silent War, fortification cloaks are spartan garments designed to instantly harden upon impact, dulling even the most dangerous attacks. A fortification cloak grants you a 20% chance [[/r 1d100]] to treat a critical hit you would take as a normal hit that deals normal damage and doesn’t apply any critical hit effects. The benefit granted by a fortification cloak doesn’t stack with a force field’s fortification or other similar abilities.</p>"
